('G.1.1.1', 'Programmes to Combat Bribery and Corruption', 'Do you have any programmes to combat Bribary and Corruption?', 'YNP', NULL, NULL, 'An effective Program is the entirety of an enterprise‚Äôs anti-bribery efforts and corruption, specifically including its code of ethics, policies and procedures, administrative processes, training, guidance and oversight. This commitment is to develop and administer an internal compliance Program that effectively makes an enterprise‚Äôs anti-corruption policy an integral part of daily practice.'),
