('G.1.3.5', 'Equator Principles and Related Reporting', 'Are you a signatory of the Equator Principles and related reporting?', 'YNP', NULL, NULL, 'The Equator Principles (EPs) is a credit risk management framework for determining, assessing and managing environmental and social risk in Project Finance transactions. Project Finance is often used to fund the development and construction of major infrastructure and industrial projects.'),
